EClass.Presentation.LayerObject

Class FreeLine

  • java.lang.Object
    • EClass.Presentation.LayerObject.LayerObject
      • EClass.Presentation.LayerObject.FreeLine

  • public abstract class FreeLine
extends LayerObject
    The FreeLine will represent a combination of Points to be presented onto the screen. Uses can include things such as free drawing, writing, or any other thing onto the whiteboard. points is a collection of points that will represent all points in the FreeLine. All lines in points will be presented to the Presentation.
